sheets - minimal spreadsheet
============================
sheets is a minimal terminal spreadsheet program.


Requirements
------------
In order to build sheets you need ncurses header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (sheets is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install sheets
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running sheets
--------------
See the man page for details.
